Uterus packed with sperm in inseminated females; vagina at right angle to body axis; reproductive tract hypertrophied in some specimens. Vulva a transverse slit, vulval lips raised <1 µm, small vulval plate present. Anus an obscure pore. Tail broadly conoid; length 1–2.5 times diameter at anus, tip broadly rounded to almost hemispherical (
Fig. 4J
).
